    AbstractResource
    Provides a base implementation for Resource classes.
    Actions
    Contains constants for the actions performed by the application.
    Difficulty
     
    Ingredient
    Represents the data about an ingredient.
    LogContext
    Provides the log context for the application on a per-thread basis.
    Message
    Represents a message or an error message.
    Recipe
    Represents the data about a recipe.
    RecipeIngredient

    Represents a tag for searching recipes.

    Represents the data about an user.

    Represents the a user-recipe relation (recipes liked by the user).
    UserRole
    Represents the data about the role of a user.
